#    81920       18.15         —         partial CPU offload
#
# TOOL-CALL TESTS (all passed)
# ----------------------------
#   ✓ Basic single tool call            — empty content, correct args
#   ✓ Multi-turn (tool result → reply)  — correct natural language reply
#   ✓ Content consistency (5/5 runs)    — all empty content, zero preamble
#   ✓ opencode system prompt override   — no issues
#
# COMPARISON vs OTHER MODELS IN THIS SUITE (P40, 2026-05-02)
# -----------------------------------------------------------
#   model                  gen tok/s  max VRAM ctx  tool call quality
#   -----                  ---------  ------------  -----------------
#   gemma4:26b                 44.62       77824    excellent (5/5 clean)
#   qwen3-coder:30b-a3b        52.83       49152    good (needs SYSTEM fix)
